Happy Mother’s Day to the most incredible woman I know❤️Words will never be enough to express how deeply grateful I am for everything you’ve done for me. From the sleepless nights to the countless sacrifices you made without hesitation, you showed me the true meaning of unconditional love. You’ve been my safe place, my biggest supporter, my silent strength, and the heart of our home. Your love has shaped who I am, your wisdom has guided my steps, and your courage has inspired me more than you’ll ever know. No matter how old I get, I’ll always need your hugs, your advice, and your love. Today and every day, I celebrate you—not just as my mother, but as the extraordinary human being you are. Thank you for being my everything. I love you more than words can say. 😘
